text: Freema Agyeman (born Frema Agyeman on 20 March 1979) is an English actress. She is of Ghanaian and Iranian descent. She is known by a lot of people for playing Martha Jones on the television series Doctor Who and also in its spin- off series Torchwood. == References == Category:1979 births Category:Black British actors Category:Living people Category:English television actors Category:Actors from London
